"{\"uid\": \"ealingtimes.co.uk-news-24432888.cunningham-using-self-belief-fuel-maiden-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Sport  Caden Cunningham admits that when he steps onto the mat to face taekwondo heavyweights who are half a foot taller than him, a little trepidation goes through his mind.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 174, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13, \"end\": 23, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"score\": 0.9951037477417275, \"rank\": 0.00467119154303306, \"text\": \"Cunningham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, the 21-year-old from Huddersfield reminds himself that he is more than capable of achieving his aim of becoming the youngest Olympic heavyweight champion in his sport and goes out there to kick them in the face.\", \"from\": 176, \"to\": 393, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 203, \"end\": 215, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huddersfield\", \"score\": 0.8685538454860646, \"rank\": 0.15117323811096467, \"text\": \"Huddersfield\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huddersfield\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huddersfield\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You need a certain level of confidence to succeed in a sport where kicks to the head are not only allowed but encouraged, and Cunningham is planning to use that belief to fuel him to Olympic glory.\", \"from\": 395, \"to\": 592, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 521, \"end\": 531, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"score\": 0.9951037477417275, \"rank\": 0.00467119154303306, \"text\": \"Cunningham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said: \\\"You think 'Oh my god, oh my god, oh my god, he's massive!'\", \"from\": 594, \"to\": 662, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Then as soon as I get there, I put my headguard on, I get in the mindset of 'I am going to kick you in the face'.\", \"from\": 663, \"to\": 776, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For me, it's about building an ego and pride when you get into the ring.\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 851, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A lot of these guys are bigger and older than me.\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 901, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am not small, but I am not a big heavyweight.\", \"from\": 902, \"to\": 949, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Most of these have five or six inches on me, and ten years' experience.\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 1021, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So most fights I am the underdog and I go out there and think, I will kick you in the face, let us get it on.\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1131, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For anyone to go to the Olympics and not go for gold, you should hold yourself to a higher standard.\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1234, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You almost want to manifest it, speak it into existence.\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1291, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But also, I decided I was going to go to these Olympics ten years ago, I did not decide I was going to go to participate, I am going to win.\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1432, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This Olympics is an opportunity to fight the best I can in front of the most people.\", \"from\": 1434, \"to\": 1519, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the biggest mental and physical challenge I will go through in my taekwondo career, so what could go wrong?\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1632, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the best opportunity I could get.\", \"from\": 1633, \"to\": 1671, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am ready to unleash everything I have been working towards.\\\"\", \"from\": 1673, \"to\": 1736, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Caden Cunningham, Rebecca McGowan and Bradly Sinden complete our taekwondo line-up!Some team \\ud83e\\udd29pic.twitter.com/1MMdQdkcCY  Cunningham's path to gold will not be easy.\", \"from\": 1738, \"to\": 1903, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1744, \"end\": 1754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"score\": 0.9951037477417275, \"rank\": 0.00467119154303306, \"text\": \"Cunningham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\"}, {\"begin\": 1756, \"end\": 1771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca_McGowan\", \"score\": 0.9999947512179875, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rebecca McGowan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca_McGowan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca_McGowan\"}, {\"begin\": 1776, \"end\": 1789, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bradly_Sinden\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bradly Sinden\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bradly_Sinden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bradly_Sinden\"}, {\"begin\": 1861, \"end\": 1871, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"score\": 0.9951037477417275, \"rank\": 0.00467119154303306, \"text\": \"Cunningham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As it stands, he could face Niger's Abdul Razzak Issoufou and Cuba's Rafael Alba in his first two fights, both former world champions and Olympic medallists.\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 2061, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1933, \"end\": 1938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Niger\", \"score\": 0.9999999523192866, \"rank\": 4.526574616899509e-08, \"text\": \"Niger\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Niger\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Niger\"}, {\"begin\": 1947, \"end\": 1953, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abdur_Razzak_(actor)\", \"score\": 0.9937100245836883, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Razzak\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abdur_Razzak_(actor)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abdur_Razzak_(actor)\"}, {\"begin\": 1967, \"end\": 1971, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cuba\", \"score\": 0.9999991530566097, \"rank\": 4.2125564939061316e-07, \"text\": \"Cuba\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cuba\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cuba\"}, {\"begin\": 1974, \"end\": 1985, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Alba\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rafael Alba\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Alba\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Alba\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Where some might be daunted by that prospect, Cunningham says bring it on.\", \"from\": 2063, \"to\": 2137, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2110, \"end\": 2120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"score\": 0.9951037477417275, \"rank\": 0.00467119154303306, \"text\": \"Cunningham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said: \\\"They are both big 6'8\\\", 6'9\\\" guys.\", \"from\": 2139, \"to\": 2183, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They are tough opponents but I rise to challenges.\", \"from\": 2184, \"to\": 2234, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If I relax and perform right, I am Olympic champion level.\", \"from\": 2235, \"to\": 2293, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am confident I will be able to show that on August 10.\", \"from\": 2294, \"to\": 2350, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel like you can never be fully prepared for something like this but I feel like I am in a good head space, I feel like I know what's coming.\", \"from\": 2352, \"to\": 2497, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am going to go out there, it's man versus man, we are going to have a fight and make sure I am the better man.\", \"from\": 2498, \"to\": 2610, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Four fights, come away with my gold and all of it will have been worth it.\\\"\", \"from\": 2611, \"to\": 2686, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Cunningham will not be short of support in the French capital, with lots of friends and family coming over.\", \"from\": 2688, \"to\": 2795, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2689, \"end\": 2699, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"score\": 0.9951037477417275, \"rank\": 0.00467119154303306, \"text\": \"Cunningham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\"}, {\"begin\": 2736, \"end\": 2742, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9858411530186668, \"rank\": 0.012498393672256372, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And he also has two housemates joining him in the Olympic Village, with world champion Bradly Sinden and Rebecca McGowan also being named by Team GB.\", \"from\": 2797, \"to\": 2946, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2848, \"end\": 2863, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 0.9999999278866224, \"rank\": 7.205161892660298e-08, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}, {\"begin\": 2903, \"end\": 2918, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca_McGowan\", \"score\": 0.9999947512179875, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rebecca McGowan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca_McGowan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca_McGowan\"}, {\"begin\": 2939, \"end\": 2946, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999999955962267, \"rank\": 2.6118976648618744e-09, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Sinden, Cunningham has the perfect role model as he looks to make Olympic history.\", \"from\": 2948, \"to\": 3033, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2960, \"end\": 2970, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"score\": 0.9951037477417275, \"rank\": 0.00467119154303306, \"text\": \"Cunningham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aldi are proud Official Partners of Team GB & ParalympicsGB, supporting all athletes through to Paris 2024  This website and associated newspapers adhere to the Independent Press Standards Organisation's     Editors' Code of Practice.\", \"from\": 3035, \"to\": 3269, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3036, \"end\": 3040, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aldi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Aldi\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aldi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aldi\"}, {\"begin\": 3132, \"end\": 3142, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.4281794666817904e-13, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you have a complaint about the editorial content which relates to     inaccuracy or intrusion, then pleasecontact the editor here.\", \"from\": 3270, \"to\": 3403, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you are dissatisfied with the response provided you cancontact IPSO here  \\u00a9 2001-2025.\", \"from\": 3408, \"to\": 3497, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Ealing Timesis owned and operated by Newsquest Media Group Ltd, an audited local newspaper network.\", \"from\": 3498, \"to\": 3601, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3540, \"end\": 3565, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newsquest\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Newsquest Media Group Ltd\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newsquest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newsquest\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Visitnewsquest.co.ukto view ourpoliciesandterms.\", \"from\": 3603, \"to\": 3651, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Echo Building, 18 Albert Road, Bournemouth, England BH1 1BZ.\", \"from\": 3653, \"to\": 3717, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3654, \"end\": 3662, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southern_Daily_Echo\", \"score\": 0.9994801516566295, \"rank\": 0.000520118726127093, \"text\": \"The Echo\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southern_Daily_Echo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southern_Daily_Echo\"}, {\"begin\": 3676, \"end\": 3682, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uncle_Albert\", \"score\": 0.9990311704143569, \"rank\": 0.0009695944777582521, \"text\": \"Albert\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uncle_Albert\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uncle_Albert\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Registered in England & Wales | 01676637  Data returned from the Piano 'meterActive/meterExpired' callbackevent.\", \"from\": 3718, \"to\": 3830, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As a subscriber, you are shown80% lessdisplay advertising when reading our                     articles.\", \"from\": 3832, \"to\": 3936, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Those ads you do see are predominantly fromlocal businessespromotinglocal                         services.\", \"from\": 3938, \"to\": 4045, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These adverts enable local businesses to get in front of their target audience - thelocal                         community.\", \"from\": 4047, \"to\": 4171, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is important that we continue to promote these adverts as our local businesses need                     as much support as possible during these challenging times.\", \"from\": 4173, \"to\": 4339, \"entities\": []}]}"